  "names": [
    {
      "full_name": "So-called \"Luhansk People's Republic\"",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "The so-called “Luhansk People’s Republic” was established on 27 April 2014. Responsible for organising the illegal referendum on 11 May 2014. Declaration of independence on 12 May 2014. On 22 May 2014, the so-called “People’s Republics” of Donetsk and Luhansk created the so-called “Federal State of Novorossiya”. This is in breach of Ukrainian constitutional law, and, as a consequence, of international law, thus undermining the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine. In October 2022, the so-called “Luhansk People’s Republic” was annexed by the Russian Federation, constituting a further violation of the territorial integrity of Ukraine and hence of international law.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}